*"Čudna* situacija se dogodila na parkingu." (An odd situation happened in the parking lot.)

*"Ona se ponaša čudno* prema meni." (She behaves oddly towards me.)

*"Videli smo čudno* oblako." (We saw a strange cloud.)

*"Njegov pogled bio je čudan*." (His look was strange.)

*"Njegovo ponašanje bilo je čudno*." (His behaviour was weird.)

*"Čudnu* situaciju smo svi doživeli." (We all experienced a strange situation.)